query:
INSERT INTO parentChildren (parentUserId, studentId, relationship, createdAt)
SELECT pu.id, s.id, 'parent', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
FROM users pu
CROSS JOIN students s
JOIN users su ON s.userId = su.id
WHERE pu.name LIKE '%桂真%' AND su.name LIKE '%山田%' AND pu.role = 'parent';
